<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
        <h1>LTI Toolkit Example</h1>
        <p>Connect to this tool using LTI 1.0 or LTI 1.3 to continue</p>
        <hr />
        <h2>LTI 1.3 Example</h2>
        <p>LTI 1.3 requires additional configuration.</p>
        <p><a href="admin">Access LTI 1.3 Configuration Page</a></p>
        <hr />
        <h2>LTI 1.0 Example</h2>
        <p>Settings:
        <ul>
          <li><b>LTI Key:</b> <pre style="display: inline">{{ key }}</pre></li>
          <li><b>LTI Secret:</b> <pre style="display: inline">{{ secret }}</pre></li>
          <li><b>XML Configuration URL:</b> <pre style="display: inline">{{ domain }}/lti/provider/config.xml</pre></li>
          <li><b>Launch/Redirect URL:</b> <pre style="display: inline">{{ domain }}/lti/provider/launch</pre></li>
          <li><b>Privacy: </b> Any privacy level is supported ("Public" gives all student data, "Anonymous" hides most student data)
        </ul>
        <h3>Canvas LTI 1.0 Example Screenshots</h3>
        <p>XML Configuration</p>
        <img src="/images/lti10xml.png" style="border:1px solid black" />
        <br>
        <p>Manual Configuration</p>
        <img src="/images/lti10.png" style="border:1px solid black" />
        <br>
        <p>Assignment Configuration</p>
        <img src="/images/lti10assign.png" style="border:1px solid black" />
        </p>
        
    </main>
  </body>
</html>